    "name": "Times Newswire API",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "description": {
      "content": "With the Times Newswire API, you can get links and metadata for Times' articles as soon as they are published on NYTimes.com. The Times Newswire API provides an up-to-the-minute stream of published articles.  You can filter results by source (all, nyt, or iht) and section (arts, business, ...).\n```\n/content/{source}/{section}.json\n```\n## Example Call\n```\nhttps://api.nytimes.com/svc/news/v3/content/all/all.json?api-key=yourkey\n```\n",
      "type": "text/plain"
